00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:05,960
Xia.

299
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,030
Xia.

300
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:08,750
Now go.

301
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:09,440
My boyfriend is coming.

302
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,030
I don't want to be misunderstood.

303
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:10,840
Wait, Bai Xia,

304
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,600
Now go.

305
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,510
Xia.

306
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:27,960
Who was that guy just now?

307
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:32,030
What's up?

308
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,750
Your coworker?

309
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:39,960
Xu Mingli.

310
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,600
We've broken up.

311
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,390
I know,

312
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,240
but as a friend,

313
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:45,550
I can still visit you.

314
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,000
I've thought it over.

315
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,000
First,

316
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:49,000
I promise you

317
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,360
Nuo will never dare to mess with you again.

318
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,840
If she dares to do that,

319
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,200
I'll teach her a lesson.

320
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,440
Second, about the money,

321
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:56,720
I really took care of it for you.

322
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,630
Xu Mingli.

323
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,510
I'm tired of hearing

324
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:02,000
these words from you.

325
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:03,600
Since I fell in love with you,

326
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,200
except for hostility and slander from others,

327
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,240
what do I have?

328
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:10,200
Just that house?

329
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,390
I'll give it back to you.

330
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:13,750
We'll be even.

331
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,240
Houses

332
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:17,080
and possessions are just material.

333
00:16:17,870 --> 00:16:19,120
What do we need?

334
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,000
Love and affection.

335
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:22,510
There's still love between us.

336
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,240
Love?

337
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,360
Yes.

338
00:16:29,030 --> 00:16:30,550
And because of that love,

339
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:32,720
in a man's opinion,

340
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,080
a woman doesn't deserve to talk about money,

341
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,510
right?

342
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,030
No.

343
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,320
Xu Mingli.

344
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,550
I want

345
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,630
a stable family

346
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,870
and a husband

347
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,320
who can support my career with money,

348
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:50,790
and you

349
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,670
want a wife with beauty

350
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,480
and intelligence.

351
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:57,870
I thought we were a strong couple.

352
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,670
We certainly are.

353
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:02,080
You're my ideal wife.

354
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:03,910
Stop fooling me.

355
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,200
- I'm not. - Xu Mingli.

356
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,070
You're a businessman.

357
00:17:09,350 --> 00:17:10,640
No investment, no return.

358
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,590
You know that better than I do.

359
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:21,920
Xia.

360
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:25,480
I didn't realize you were soberer

361
00:17:25,550 --> 00:17:26,680
than I thought.

362
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,640
I came here today with much sincerity.

363
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,920
I've thought it over.

364
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,920
Will you marry me?

365
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,350
Marry me, Xia.

366
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:55,270
Can I trust you again?

367
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,920
Of course.

368
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,310
And I promise you

369
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,240
that when we get married,

370
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:03,920
you can move in here and live with me,

371
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:04,790
okay?

372
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:06,000
You can leave the original villa

373
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:06,880
to your mom.

374
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,750
I'll do what you say in the future.

375
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:09,590
I'll settle the need for money

376
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,750
and all your company debts

377
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:11,680
for you.

378
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:14,350
You swear?

379
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:15,790
I swear.

380
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,550
I'll do

381
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:18,510
what I said,

382
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,590
or I'll die.

383
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:22,830
Okay?

384
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:24,200
Don't cry, baby.

385
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:41,620
♪I love you, love you, love you♪

386
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:50,570
♪'Til I forget who I am♪

387
00:18:50,670 --> 00:18:56,290
♪I miss you, miss you, miss you♪
